  Title: Inventory!?!?!?!??!
  Description: "This 1.25ft^3 cardboard box is the perfect home for your new shiny
    dice. \nYou can place them in here simply by dragging them in from your precious
    egg carton (hotbar) and left clicking, then you can take them out by left clicking
    them and dragging it into your egg carton. \nYou can also pull dice around in
    your inventory by holding right click and if you scroll while pulling you can
    increase the range."
